        <p style="font-size:0.8rem;opacity:0.4;line-height:1.6;max-width:200px;margin:0 auto;">Any live website — yours, a competitor's, a prospect's.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center;position:relative;">
        <div style="width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(232,180,176,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(232,180,176,0.15);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:1.2rem;">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E8B4B0" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 2v4M12 18v4M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83M16.24 16.24l2.83 2.83M2 12h4M18 12h4"/></svg>
