        <p style="font-weight:600;font-size:0.95rem;margin-bottom:0.4rem;">AI scans & scores</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.8rem;opacity:0.4;line-height:1.6;max-width:200px;margin:0 auto;">30+ signals extracted. AI analyses across 5 categories in real-time.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center;position:relative;">
        <div style="width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(232,180,176,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(232,180,176,0.15);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:1.2rem;">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E8B4B0" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6"/><path d="M16 13H8M16 17H8M10 9H8"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p style="font-weight:600;font-size:0.95rem;margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Get your action plan</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.8rem;opacity:0.4;line-height:1.6;max-width:200px;margin:0 auto;">Prioritised findings with specific code-level fixes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

